<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Itinerary</h2>
<p class="p1">A superb overview of the Austrian Tyrol, and an ideal chance for walkers to explore the contrasting hiking terrain in different valleys, from gentle flower filled meadows to beautiful lakeside paths and dramatic Alpine trails with great views. We start with a gentle introduction in the rolling green hills of<strong> <a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053}" target="_blank" title="Seefeld"><strong>Seefeld</strong></a></strong>, where you can join an Inghams Wanderwalk, before transferring onto peaceful<strong> <a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/b5e429a18c1341518ff1c75889b2f4ea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b5e429a18c1341518ff1c75889b2f4ea}" target="_blank" title="Pertisau"><strong>Pertisau</strong></a> </strong>on the scenic western shores of the emerald Lake Achensee, Tyrol's largest lake. Here you can relax in the lakefront cafés, take a steam train ride, walk some more in the many trails above the village or enjoy a twilight cruise on the lake. On Saturday, transfer to Alpbach village by direct taxi (30 minutes), said to be the most picturesque in the whole of Austria, where you can join free guided walks or simply sit and soak up the views from your hotel. Finish your holiday in lively Mayrhofen (direct taxi transfer 40 minutes) which offers an unrivalled range of activities, excursions and events through the summer.</p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>What’s included</h2>
<p>Prices include flights, resort transfers, accommodation and services of Inghams Rep.</p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Accommodation</h2>
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>Seefeld</strong></td>
<td>***</td>
<td><a data-udi="umb://document/f22accd14a174a4386f2a6b0f87400ee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f22accd14a174a4386f2a6b0f87400ee}" title="Hotel Stefanie">Hotel Stefanie</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Pertisau</strong></td>
<td>**</td>
<td><a data-udi="umb://document/dd07c1f47a9d4653be213a22bbbe355e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dd07c1f47a9d4653be213a22bbbe355e}" title="Hotel-Garni Klara">Pension Klara</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Alpbach</strong></td>
<td>**½</td>
<td><a data-udi="umb://document/54138a60086c4727a11eedf0f0cf6a03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/54138a60086c4727a11eedf0f0cf6a03}" title="Haus Edelweiss">Haus Edelweiss</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Mayrhofen</strong></td>
<td>***</td>
<td><a data-udi="umb://document/bf41b19251de453d8cd1795d8dd547cc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bf41b19251de453d8cd1795d8dd547cc}" title="Hotel Landhaus Roscher">Hotel Landhaus Roscher</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>Other combinations are available. Tours depart weekly on Saturdays. Services of an Inghams Rep in each resort and all transfers are included.</p>
</div>
<div>
<h2>14 nights from £899*. Please call our reservations team on 01483 79 11 11 to book this holiday</h2>
</div>
